body_html: We really appreciate this issue report, however I'm going to close it out due to inactivity. We're still open to solving this issue, but we need a simple way to reproduce it. If anyone in the community can help us out on that end, please file an issue against our new GitHub repository. Be sure to reference this issue. https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard/issues/new
